First, we will align the numbers vertically and perform the addition as follows:

\[
\begin{array}{c@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}}
 & & & 1 & 2 & 0 & 9 & 3_{13} \\
+ & & & & & 4 & 2 & 0 & 1_{13} \\
\hline
 & & & 1 & 2 & 5 & 0 & 0 & 4_{13} \\
\end{array}
\]

Therefore, \(12093_{13} + 4201_{13} = 125004_{13}\).